        "Effects": "Paladins used this spell fill their body with [[positive energy]] granted from their [[deity]]. The positive energy provided temporary boosts to health, strength, dexterity and physical hardiness. Additionally, any [[undead]] striking a paladin protected by ''righteous fury'' was harmed when the positive energy lashed out at them.",
